{"tid":1364712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無論要幾和理優都好 唔該俾人打要自衛","createTime":"2019-07-25T12:11:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T13:09:25.000Z","uid":273176,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1f3a63fbc945c183f7242e0b3d42e092bcb03267","tid":1364712,"uid":273176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:11:17.000Z","msg":"我都唔想用呢個咁柒嘅Term <br />\n不過出面好多人講<br />\n<br />\n由星期日話拆人祠堂<br />\n慢慢縮到唔入村<br />\n到而家話周街行消費 有事就走<br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係 <br />\n有條底線唔可以退<br />\n就係俾人打要自衛<br />\n<br />\n如果你星期六俾黑社會打仲戇鳩鳩企喺到<br />\n甚至即刻調頭走的話<br />\n咁不如唔好去啦<br />\n你呢種係示弱 唔係示威<br />\n<br />\n主唔主動開波可以再傾<br />\n但係比人打唔可以再退讓"},{"pid":"a2c0ef1b55a2776b46112c1156ea9b9882ee371c","tid":1364712,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:12:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e0a024da9f0774e5f581f6bd9e5b5252bb798d7","tid":1364712,"uid":273176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:16:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">俾人打要自衛</span>"},{"pid":"921ade6d92419dbb461133d7decffd88fe222f10","tid":1364712,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:19:23.000Z","msg":"不了<br />\n想俾人打"},{"pid":"c11b402a8e2f8fbfcddb6351602f5f043c849ffd","tid":1364712,"uid":273176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e0a024da9f0774e5f581f6bd9e5b5252bb798d7","tid":1364712,"uid":273176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:16:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">俾人打要自衛</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:26:26.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"d0db784a814d1bfce98a068ae656a09e46aeab60","tid":1364712,"uid":227433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:29:11.000Z","msg":"Agree"},{"pid":"fbb54b51c35238248467ad44de4898b23f004bd1","tid":1364712,"uid":266805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:30:39.000Z","msg":"比人打一定要自衛<br />\n因為係生命受到威脅"},{"pid":"6c5684